Body: Description: Hi all, Since we have decided not to renew our licenses for the Netwrix software, I was asked to have our Netwrix data/accounts purged, with an email confirmation of removal sent to our team. I believe Keith Kraemer and I are the last two that have accounts in the Netwrix portal, but it is possible I did not have previous members of our team removed from our account. Confirmation of the account/data removal can be sent to Justin.Burlando@anbbank.com and Keith.Kraemer@anbbank.com. Thank you, Justin Burlando
